  <brief_title>Study of Terlipressin Versus Placebo to Treat Hepatorenal Syndrome Type 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Phase III Study of Intravenous Terlipressin in Patients With Hepatorenal Syndrome Type 1</official_title>
  <sponsors>
